text:
(1)
Battery Park: A northward view across a corner of same, from State Street (trolley car thereon), and slightly southward of Pearl Street. Appearing across the elevated spur are the two units of the Whitehall Building; the Downtown Athletic Club; and framework of No. 21 West Street.

June 20, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, from a vantage point slightly westward.

June 20, 1930.

P. L. Sperr.
title: Manhattan: Battery Park - State Street.
